author: The Critical Drinker
description:
It's been the worst October at the box office in 30 years, but can Predator Badlands turn things around for Hollywood? And with the world's first ever female action hero Jennifer Lawrence admitting that nobody listens to celebs and their political views, will they finally stop preaching to us? Join me, MauLer, Razorfist, Reaper, Film Threat and Diabolical Souls as we find out. 

Subscribe to Razorfist: https://www.youtube.com/@TheRageaholic
Subscribe to Reaper: https://www.youtube.com/@RealReaper
Subscribe to Film Threat: https://www.youtube.com/@FilmThreat

title: Open Bar #163 - Predator Badlands, Hollywood's Red October, Celebs Abandon Politics
